  <metadata>
    <name>Sa Calobra (Spain)</name>
    <desc>Spain · 9.4 km · +668 m · 7.1% avg. Mallorca's coiling masterpiece — a road that loops under itself, climbing from the sea to Coll dels Reis. Approximate geometry anchored at the real trailhead for indoor training, not the exact road.</desc>
